{"tid":2026966,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共匪：中史考題雖政治正確 但用諷刺蔣介石漫畫做法不妥","createTime":"2020-05-21T09:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T09:16:53.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5854412c2fa03252f0157091ada811054ece4deb","tid":2026966,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:13:19.000Z","msg":"教評會質疑中史科考題引用諷刺蔣介石漫畫<br />\n21.05.2020 16:58<br />\n<br />\n中學文憑試今日考中史科。卷一其中一條必答題，展示兩款抗日戰爭時的宣傳品，其中一款是多個拳頭揮向倒地的日本軍人，寫有「萬眾一心誓滅倭寇」，另一款是日軍手持武器歡呼慶祝，寫明「徐州失陷」以及「華北華中的日軍完全連絡」，問考生是否同意日軍歡呼的觀點。<br />\n<br />\n教育評議會認為，題目有一反一正的對冲，明顯沒有單邊歌頌日本侵華的價值引導，分題又只佔3分，考生較易拿揑。不過，教評會質疑蔣介石是否壞到一個程度，需要另一條考題，引用諷刺觀感強烈的漫畫，達到提問效果，但不論提問形式如何，考題還是要以史實先行，再讓考生補述已知史實，加以解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289108&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289108%26csid%3D261_341&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsdE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=19ce981a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289108&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"413b7339ffe9a946d3be739055438135391f4766","tid":2026966,"uid":151534,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"DQ未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27db99e0836584a46bdb194c7b2c77e53a69c783","tid":2026966,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:15:18.000Z","msg":"中屎好多呢D圖好過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0658c5a7d3ce385f97123a4920fae3f97e3b8f47","tid":2026966,"uid":36441,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"老蔣清黨反共喎 咁又唔得？"},{"pid":"1c8ed5d0c63252af385938823dfd5883460d726f","tid":2026966,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-